erights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/9780097d9be33884a9b18f2151754b52.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/9780097d9be33884a9b18f2151754b52.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/9780097d9be33884a9b18f2151754b52.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Marius the dwarf stands non-plussed as I wield a flaming dagger near his head.\" data-chomp-id=\"9780097d9be33884a9b18f2151754b52\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"Marius the dwarf stands non-plussed as I wield a flaming dagger near his head.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/9780097d9be33884a9b18f2151754b52.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Obsidian Entertainment / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"9780097d9be33884a9b18f2151754b52\" data-recommend-id=\"image://9780097d9be33884a9b18f2151754b52\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Marius the dwarf stands non-plussed as I wield a flaming dagger near his head.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eDaggers are the tried-and-true weapon of a rogue, but they can be mixed and matched into any playstyle in \u003cem\u003eAvowed\u003c/em\u003e, thanks to the game’s focus on class freedom. Whether you’re a dagger user slinging spells with your other hand, or wielding a shield for some extra protection, you’d do well to grab the powerful \u003cstrong\u003eSheathed in Summer\u003c/strong\u003e dagger during the opening hours of the game. Here’s what to know about this fiery dagger and how to get it. - Billy Givens \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/avowed-dagger-sheathed-in-summer-best-rogue-build-1851767295\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/avowed-dagger-sheathed-in-summer-best-rogue-build-1851767295\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"eb135312c4ef30816f81afb6721008b8\" data-recommend-id=\"image://eb135312c4ef30816f81afb6721008b8\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Companion Kai wielding a cutlass and pistol in Avowed.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Companion Kai wielding a cutlass and pistol in Avowed.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/eb135312c4ef30816f81afb6721008b8.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/eb135312c4ef30816f81afb6721008b8.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/eb135312c4ef30816f81afb6721008b8.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Companion Kai wielding a cutlass and pistol in Avowed.\" data-chomp-id=\"eb135312c4ef30816f81afb6721008b8\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"Companion Kai wielding a cutlass and pistol in Avowed.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/eb135312c4ef30816f81afb6721008b8.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Obsidian Entertainment\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"eb135312c4ef30816f81afb6721008b8\" data-recommend-id=\"image://eb135312c4ef30816f81afb6721008b8\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Companion Kai wielding a cutlass and pistol in Avowed.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003ePicture this: You’ve just capsized and crashlanded on a remote island with a fort looming overhead. You’re defenseless, and a strange blue being is sifting through your ship’s remnants. You need a weapon, and in the moment, anything will suffice, like the dagger or wand on the ground before you. That’s all good, but a bit of wood and steel won’t suffice for long. You need to upgrade your weapons and armor in \u003cem\u003eAvowed\u003c/em\u003e if you wish to go toe-to-toe with some of Eora’s fearsome beasts. Here’s how I survived untold encounters with a better weapon and a bit of fire magic. - Brandon Morgan \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/avowed-how-to-upgrade-weapons-armor-guide-obsidian-rpg-1851767772\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/avowed-how-to-upgrade-weapons-armor-guide-obsidian-rpg-1851767772\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"1cf63d2c523558b4a9f25356eb1e0ab7\" data-recommend-id=\"image://1cf63d2c523558b4a9f25356eb1e0ab7\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Red beams of magic sweep the battlefield in Path of Exile 2.\" data